00:49:56,670 --> 00:50:01,854
Hey, I wanted to ask about non-fighting game franchises crossing over to fighting games.

1210
00:50:02,194 --> 00:50:04,756
How much of a factor do you think that would be for the future?

1211
00:50:05,057 --> 00:50:07,899
Because I got into fighting games because of Persona 4 Arena,

1212
00:50:08,059 --> 00:50:10,641
and then by extension Under Night In-Birth, and then Blaze Blue.

