00:50:21,510 --> 00:50:23,432
but like I think we're already there, right? Like you...

1217
00:50:24,219 --> 00:50:26,561
Basically, it's very difficult to find a fighting game that

1218
00:50:26,601 --> 00:50:27,882
has no guest characters in it right now.

1219
00:50:30,364 --> 00:50:32,225
So yeah, I mean, I think that's kind of been

1220
00:50:32,245 --> 00:50:35,428
something we've kind of seen in the last five, six years

1221
00:50:35,928 --> 00:50:37,049
kind of become almost ubiquitous.

1222
00:50:37,349 --> 00:50:37,810
I think it's great.

1223
00:50:37,850 --> 00:50:40,092
I mean, one of the great things about fighting games

1224
00:50:40,132 --> 00:50:41,212
